# Privacy Policy for Shubh Frame

**App Name:** Shubh Frame
**Contact Email:** indian.insect.killer@gmail.com

## 1. Introduction

Shubh Frame respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how our app handles information when you use Shubh Frame to create photo frames, posters, advertisements, personal templates, greeting images, and short videos.

By using Shubh Frame, you agree to this Privacy Policy.

## 2. Information We Collect

Shubh Frame does not require users to create an account or provide personal information to use the main editing features.

The app may access the following data only when required for app functionality:

* Photos selected by the user
* Videos or media files selected by the user, if applicable
* Images or videos saved by the user
* Text, stickers, emojis, and design elements added by the user
* Device storage or gallery access permissions

## 3. Photo and Media Access

Shubh Frame requests photo and media permissions so users can:

* Select photos from the device gallery
* Add photos to frames and templates
* Create personalized images and videos
* Save final designs to the device gallery
* Share generated images or videos

The app accesses only the media selected by the user or allowed through device permissions.

## 4. How We Use Your Information

The photos, text, and design content you add are used only to create your selected designs, images, frames, posters, advertisements, or videos.

We use media access only for:

* Loading selected photos into the editor
* Creating customized designs
* Generating image or video outputs
* Saving completed designs to your gallery
* Sharing the final output when you choose to share it

## 5. Data Storage

Shubh Frame processes user-created designs on the user’s device.

Unless specifically stated otherwise, your selected photos, edited images, and generated videos are not uploaded to our server by the app. Final images or videos may be saved locally on your device when you choose to save them.

Some app preferences, such as accepted disclaimer status or basic local settings, may be stored locally on your device to improve the app experience.

## 6. Sharing of Information

Shubh Frame does not sell, rent, or trade your personal information.

Your generated images or videos are shared only when you choose to share them through your device’s sharing options, such as messaging apps, social media apps, email, or other installed applications.

Once you share content through third-party apps, their privacy policies and terms will apply.

## 7. Third-Party Services

Shubh Frame may use platform services or libraries required for app functionality, such as media selection, media saving, image processing, video playback, or sharing.

If the app uses any third-party analytics, advertising, cloud storage, or AI generation services in the future, this Privacy Policy should be updated to clearly describe those services and how data is handled.

## 8. User Responsibility

Users are responsible for the photos, logos, text, business information, personal details, and other content they upload or use in the app.

Users must ensure they have the right or permission to use any uploaded content. Users should not create or share content that violates copyright, trademark, privacy, publicity, or any third-party rights.

Users must not use the app to create illegal, harmful, misleading, offensive, abusive, defamatory, obscene, discriminatory, or rights-infringing content.

## 9. Children’s Privacy

Shubh Frame is intended for general users. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

If a parent or guardian believes that a child has provided personal information through the app, they may contact us so appropriate action can be taken.

## 10. App Permissions

Depending on your device and Android/iOS version, Shubh Frame may request permissions such as:

* Photo library access
* Media access
* Save to gallery permission
* Storage access, where required by older Android versions

These permissions are used only to provide app features such as selecting photos, creating designs, saving images, and saving videos.

You can manage or revoke app permissions from your device settings at any time. Some features may not work properly if required permissions are denied.

## 11. Data Security

We take reasonable steps to protect user data handled within the app. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is completely secure. Users should avoid adding sensitive personal, financial, or confidential information to designs unless they are comfortable saving or sharing it.

## 12. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected by updating the effective date at the top of this policy.

Users are encouraged to review this Privacy Policy periodically.

